    public class ResourcesServiceImpl
extends BaseHeatServices
implements ResourcesService
    This class implements some methods for manipulation of HeatResource objects. The non-exhaustive list of methods is oriented along http://developer.openstack.org/api-ref-orchestration-v1.html
